nodes.text: Star Wars Helmet Collection 23 is the twenty-third issue of Star Wars Helmet Collection, published by De Agostini. The issue includes a 1:5 scale replica of a Rebel commando helmet.
The homeworld of Athgar Heece, Dybrin 12, is stated to be a planet. However, Star Wars: Aliens of the Galaxy classified Dybrin 12 as a moon.
